WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:06.880
Canned cherries without sugar in their own juice.

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:10.240
Hello everybody!

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:15.600
Near our house there is a cherry orchard.

00:00:15.780 --> 00:00:22.580
We harvested.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:35.440
Today we will preserve cherries in their own juice.

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:47.420
First the bones are removed from the cherries.

00:00:47.580 --> 00:00:54.120
To remove the bones using special tools.

00:00:54.220 --> 00:01:01.300
If the device can not be bought - used wooden stick.

00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:17.560
Cherries are superimposed into clean glass jars.

00:01:17.720 --> 00:01:22.920
Net Bank need baking soda.

00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:29.800
Not suitable for cleaning cans detergents containing surfactants.

00:01:41.380 --> 00:01:47.660
When filling jars cherries will produce juice.

00:01:55.640 --> 00:02:01.660
Cherries should be compacted with a spoon.

00:02:27.940 --> 00:02:34.180
Bank filled with cherries, so that the neck is left up to 3 cm.

00:02:34.260 --> 00:02:41.260
Cherry sterilization will increase in volume.

00:02:44.220 --> 00:02:50.200
Banks with cherries are placed on a sheet of electric oven.

00:02:59.887 --> 00:03:05.707
Twist impossible.

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:32.660
Banks with cherries are put in the oven to the second level from the bottom.

00:03:37.620 --> 00:03:44.400
The oven is switched on heating to 150 degrees Celsius.

00:03:44.460 --> 00:03:51.000
Index mode to stand on the top and bottom heating.

00:03:56.320 --> 00:04:01.420
Passed 1:00.

00:04:01.540 --> 00:04:05.160
The banks showed signs of boiling.

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:10.660
More air bubbles in the cherry juice.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:22.860
Banks have to stand in the oven for another 20 minutes.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:32.680
It took 20 minutes.

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:35.520
The oven is turned off.

00:04:35.660 --> 00:04:41.380
Took out a jar of boiling cherries.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:56.380
Took out a jar of boiling cherries.
Immediately twist until it stops.

00:05:07.340 --> 00:05:13.100
Banks are required to cool at room temperature.

00:05:13.100 --> 00:05:17.020
Canned cherries are used as fillings in the manufacture of food products.

00:05:17.040 --> 00:05:19.200
From these it can be cooked cherries compote.

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:23.200
Thank you for watching!

